From: Leo Liu <leo.liu@amd.com>
Date: Tue, 3 Dec 2019 09:18:51 -0500
Subject: drm/amdgpu: enable VCN3.0 PG and CG for Sienna_Cichlid
Git-commit: e823be13dbc2523663b3b2a13e94863252f6fba9
Patch-mainline: v5.9-rc1
References: jsc#SLE-12680, jsc#SLE-12880, jsc#SLE-12882, jsc#SLE-12883, jsc#SLE-13496, jsc#SLE-15322

By setting up the flags to the ASIC

Signed-off-by: Leo Liu <leo.liu@amd.com>
Reviewed-by: James Zhu <James.Zhu@amd.com>
Acked-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Alex Deucher <alexander.deucher@amd.com>
Signed-off-by: Patrik Jakobsson <pjakobsson@suse.de>
---
 drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c | 4 ++--
 1 file changed, 2 insertions(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
index 587d0b6821f8..80428ae470c1 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/amd/amdgpu/nv.c
@@ -710,8 +710,8 @@ static int nv_common_early_init(void *handle)
 		adev->external_rev_id = adev->rev_id + 0xa;
 		break;
 	case CHIP_SIENNA_CICHLID:
-		adev->cg_flags = 0;
-		adev->pg_flags = 0;
+		adev->cg_flags = AMD_CG_SUPPORT_VCN_MGCG;
+		adev->pg_flags = AMD_PG_SUPPORT_VCN;
 		adev->external_rev_id = adev->rev_id + 0x28;
 		break;
 	default:
